[SPEAKER_00] najveći zaštitnik u boju,

1542
01:32:15,100 --> 01:32:16,260
[SPEAKER_00] onaj koji je,

1543
01:32:16,260 --> 01:32:17,619
[SPEAKER_00] znamo što je napravio,

1544
01:32:17,619 --> 01:32:20,399
[SPEAKER_00] kome je otkinuo glavu.

1545
01:32:20,399 --> 01:32:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] Molim vas,

1546
01:32:21,500 --> 01:32:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] može jedna poruka

1547
01:32:22,420 --> 01:32:23,819
[SPEAKER_00] za našeg gledatelje

1548
01:32:23,819 --> 01:32:24,899
[SPEAKER_00] podcasta Mrežnica,

1549
01:32:24,899 --> 01:32:26,279
[SPEAKER_00] kako da svatko od nas

1550
01:32:26,279 --> 01:32:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] živi dan

1551
01:32:27,579 --> 01:32:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] ujutro od kad otvori oči,

1552
01:32:29,779 --> 01:32:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] tijekom celog dana,

1553
01:32:30,880 --> 01:32:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa na večer,

1554
01:32:31,699 --> 01:32:33,939
[SPEAKER_00] dok ide na počinak.

1555
01:32:34,260 --> 01:32:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] Kako da taj dan

1556
01:32:35,340 --> 01:32:36,739
[SPEAKER_00] nam bude posvećen?

1557
01:32:36,739 --> 01:32:37,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako,

1558
01:32:37,640 --> 01:32:38,520
[SPEAKER_01] reći se tu.

1559
01:32:38,520 --> 01:32:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] Najprije mi se nalazimo

1560
01:32:40,920 --> 01:32:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] što se tiče

1561
01:32:41,659 --> 01:32:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] onih četiri

1562
01:32:42,659 --> 01:32:45,100
[SPEAKER_01] iz apokolipce.

1563
01:32:45,100 --> 01:32:45,720
[SPEAKER_01] Jahača.

1564
01:32:45,720 --> 01:32:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jahača.

1565
01:32:46,460 --> 01:32:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo kad se pažljivije čita,

1566
01:32:49,199 --> 01:32:50,739
[SPEAKER_01] vidi se zapravo

1567
01:32:50,739 --> 01:32:51,500
[SPEAKER_01] što ti

1568
01:32:51,500 --> 01:32:54,479
[SPEAKER_01] konji predstavljaju.

1569
01:32:54,479 --> 01:32:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] Konji predstavljaju tu silu,

1570
01:32:56,079 --> 01:32:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] jednu nadljudsku silu,

1571
01:32:58,539 --> 01:33:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno demonsku snagu.

1572
01:33:00,039 --> 01:33:01,739
[SPEAKER_01] To treba simbolički razumijeti.

1573
01:33:01,739 --> 01:33:03,300
[SPEAKER_01] Prva je

1574
01:33:03,300 --> 01:33:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] kupovanje,

1575
01:33:04,739 --> 01:33:05,439
[SPEAKER_01] prodavanje,

1576
01:33:05,439 --> 01:33:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] dakle ekonomija.

1577
01:33:06,359 --> 01:33:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ekonomska iscrpljivanja,

1578
01:33:08,039 --> 01:33:09,399
[SPEAKER_01] ekonomske krize je ovako.

1579
01:33:09,399 --> 01:33:10,899
[SPEAKER_01] Druga,

1580
01:33:10,899 --> 01:33:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] bit će

1581
01:33:14,659 --> 01:33:19,619
[SPEAKER_01] dignut mir sa zemlje.

1582
01:33:19,619 --> 01:33:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] Znači uznemirani će svi biti.

1583
01:33:23,800 --> 01:33:26,020
[SPEAKER_01] To su ti sukobi podijele i tako.

1584
01:33:26,779 --> 01:33:28,520
[SPEAKER_01] I niko se neće osjećati siguran.

1585
01:33:28,520 --> 01:33:29,659
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je treća?

1586
01:33:29,659 --> 01:33:30,920
[SPEAKER_01] Sad sam zaboravio.

1587
01:33:30,920 --> 01:33:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] A četvrtom je...

1588
01:33:33,920 --> 01:33:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] Treći Jahače nosi glad i bolest.

1589
01:33:36,159 --> 01:33:37,060
[SPEAKER_01] E da.

1590
01:33:37,060 --> 01:33:39,340
[SPEAKER_01] Zar to nije bilo?

1591
01:33:39,340 --> 01:33:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sa ovim, počevši od koronavirusom,

1592
01:33:42,000 --> 01:33:43,140
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je bolest,

1593
01:33:43,140 --> 01:33:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] na jedan put sav svijet je,

1594
01:33:44,840 --> 01:33:46,939
[SPEAKER_01] užasno bolestan umrijećeš

1595
01:33:46,939 --> 01:33:48,279
[SPEAKER_01] i još prognoziraju

1596
01:33:48,279 --> 01:33:50,260
[SPEAKER_01] da će još strašnije stvari doći

1597
01:33:50,260 --> 01:33:53,079
[SPEAKER_01] i već kažu da rade na cijepivima.

1598
01:33:53,079 --> 01:33:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kako radiš cijepivo za nešto

1599
01:33:54,699 --> 01:33:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] što još nije došlo?

1600
01:33:55,619 --> 01:33:58,779
[SPEAKER_01] Medicina je postala

1601
01:33:58,779 --> 01:34:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] jedna isto vrsta oružja

1602
01:34:00,840 --> 01:34:02,180
[SPEAKER_01] mikroorganizmima.

1603
01:34:02,180 --> 01:34:04,479
[SPEAKER_01] Mikrobiologija je sad u ključu.

1604
01:34:04,479 --> 01:34:06,880
[SPEAKER_01] Razgovarao sam s jednim mladićem

1605
01:34:06,880 --> 01:34:08,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji je

1606
01:34:08,239 --> 01:34:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] stručnjak iz

1607
01:34:09,800 --> 01:34:11,579
[SPEAKER_01] te fotonike

1608
01:34:11,579 --> 01:34:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] dok je posao negdje tamo

1609
01:34:14,039 --> 01:34:15,439
[SPEAKER_01] i pa sam pitao što radite.

1610
01:34:15,600 --> 01:34:17,600
[SPEAKER_01] Pa pravimo se, bavimo se ovom

1611
01:34:17,600 --> 01:34:19,779
[SPEAKER_01] modernom medicinom.

1612
01:34:19,779 --> 01:34:21,319
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže,

1613
01:34:21,319 --> 01:34:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] Marko, šta ti imaš s time,

1614
01:34:22,920 --> 01:34:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] sa laserima spojim?

1615
01:34:23,960 --> 01:34:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] A kaže, ne, nego

1616
01:34:25,699 --> 01:34:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] na taj način

1617
01:34:28,199 --> 01:34:30,819
[SPEAKER_01] uz pomoć laserskih snage zraka

1618
01:34:30,819 --> 01:34:32,359
[SPEAKER_01] mi možemo poticati

1619
01:34:32,359 --> 01:34:34,479
[SPEAKER_01] bakterije i viruse

1620
01:34:34,479 --> 01:34:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] da se brže razvodnožavaju

1621
01:34:36,460 --> 01:34:37,399
[SPEAKER_01] ili sporije

1622
01:34:37,399 --> 01:34:39,600
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu na neke druge

1623
01:34:39,600 --> 01:34:41,979
[SPEAKER_01] i onda pravimo taj kombinaciju

1624
01:34:41,979 --> 01:34:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] da dobijemo zadovaljajući lijek.

1625
01:34:43,920 --> 01:34:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako možeš napraviti

1626
01:34:45,460 --> 01:34:47,140
[SPEAKER_01] da ozdraviš na bolje

1627
01:34:47,140 --> 01:34:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] ko kaže

1628
01:34:48,539 --> 01:34:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] da ne možeš napraviti

1629
01:34:49,960 --> 01:34:51,619
[SPEAKER_01] i da potruješ narode

1630
01:34:51,619 --> 01:34:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] na taj način.

1631
01:34:52,460 --> 01:34:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1632
01:34:53,180 --> 01:34:54,359
[SPEAKER_01] I tu se znači

1633
01:34:54,359 --> 01:34:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] navješćuje se smrti

1634
01:34:56,180 --> 01:34:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo je vrijeme smrti.

1635
01:34:57,180 --> 01:34:58,760
[SPEAKER_00] To je onaj četvrti jahač

1636
01:34:58,760 --> 01:34:59,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji jedni ima ime.

1637
01:34:59,880 --> 01:35:01,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ima mu je smrti.

1638
01:35:01,460 --> 01:35:03,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ima mu je smrti.

1639
01:35:03,220 --> 01:35:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je vrijeme smrti.

1640
01:35:04,340 --> 01:35:05,680
[SPEAKER_01] Na sve načine

1641
01:35:05,680 --> 01:35:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] se želi uništiti čovječanstvo

1642
01:35:07,779 --> 01:35:09,560
[SPEAKER_01] ali ga neće uništiti nitko.

1643
01:35:10,920 --> 01:35:13,439
[SPEAKER_01] Oni kaže, daj moli što je potrebno moliti

1644
01:35:13,439 --> 01:35:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] da se spasi kršćanska Evropa.

1645
01:35:15,880 --> 01:35:17,100
[SPEAKER_01] Tako mi je rekao biskup.

1646
01:35:17,100 --> 01:35:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja čim sam izišao,

1647
01:35:20,000 --> 01:35:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] već mi je došla riječ.

1648
01:35:21,140 --> 01:35:22,819
[SPEAKER_01] Potrebno je

1649
01:35:22,819 --> 01:35:26,140
[SPEAKER_01] da se crkva pokaje

1650
01:35:26,140 --> 01:35:28,100
[SPEAKER_01] za sudjelovanje

1651
01:35:28,100 --> 01:35:29,939
[SPEAKER_01] u zločinu humanizma

1652
01:35:29,939 --> 01:35:33,600
[SPEAKER_01] koji je odvratio moju djecu

1653
01:35:33,600 --> 01:35:35,319
[SPEAKER_01] od moga nauka

1654
01:35:35,319 --> 01:35:37,640
[SPEAKER_01] svjetovnoj poprilici.

1655
01:35:37,640 --> 01:35:39,140
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ovo ne govorim doslovce

1656
01:35:39,140 --> 01:35:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] kako piše tamo.

1657
01:35:40,840 --> 01:35:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže, od tada su počeli slušati svijet,

1658
01:35:44,340 --> 01:35:46,520
[SPEAKER_01] a ne moje svete.

1659
01:35:46,520 --> 01:35:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog toga ne mogu svijet pobjediti,

1660
01:35:49,699 --> 01:35:51,220
[SPEAKER_01] nego svijet pobjeđuje njih.

1661
01:35:51,220 --> 01:35:53,279
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, potrebno je

1662
01:35:53,279 --> 01:35:56,140
[SPEAKER_01] da se pokaju za grijeh

1663
01:35:56,140 --> 01:35:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] i prinesu žrtvu

1664
01:35:58,500 --> 01:35:59,859
[SPEAKER_01] zadovoljštine.

1665
01:35:59,859 --> 01:36:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] Nažalost, nisam šuo niko

1666
01:36:03,359 --> 01:36:04,659
[SPEAKER_01] da to tako nešto čini.

1667
01:36:04,659 --> 01:36:06,380
[SPEAKER_01] I ali onda

1668
01:36:06,380 --> 01:36:08,819
[SPEAKER_01] nemati druge, nego dogodit će se

1669
01:36:08,819 --> 01:36:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve što je prijetnja

1670
01:36:10,000 --> 01:36:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Džavolska napravila,

1671
01:36:11,500 --> 01:36:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] ako nećeš Božje nešto.

1672
01:36:13,340 --> 01:36:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kako da se sami spasimo?

1673
01:36:14,920 --> 01:36:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ovako, kako se ja spašavam,

1674
01:36:17,579 --> 01:36:19,060
[SPEAKER_01] ovo govorim iz iskustva.

1675
01:36:19,060 --> 01:36:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] Eto.

1676
01:36:19,640 --> 01:36:22,640
[SPEAKER_01] Najprije što se tiče rata.

1677
01:36:24,260 --> 01:36:26,060
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je počeo vrat,

1678
01:36:26,060 --> 01:36:26,600
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam mislio,

1679
01:36:26,600 --> 01:36:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, drage, kako ostati živ

1680
01:36:28,079 --> 01:36:29,020
[SPEAKER_01] uopće u ovome,

1681
01:36:29,020 --> 01:36:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] ovoj vrijeme,

1682
01:36:30,180 --> 01:36:31,600
[SPEAKER_01] ubojica, razbojnika,

1683
01:36:31,600 --> 01:36:33,359
[SPEAKER_01] bludnika, vračara,

1684
01:36:33,359 --> 01:36:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam kakvih sve nema.

1685
01:36:34,720 --> 01:36:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] Sve sam ih imao.

1686
01:36:36,279 --> 01:36:37,220
[SPEAKER_01] Napadali su na mene,

1687
01:36:37,220 --> 01:36:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] pisali su mu prijeteća pisma

1688
01:36:39,619 --> 01:36:40,979
[SPEAKER_01] da će nabiti mene

1689
01:36:40,979 --> 01:36:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] i mojih pet okota

1690
01:36:42,180 --> 01:36:44,020
[SPEAKER_01] na kolac i izbaciti iz Hrvatske,

1691
01:36:44,020 --> 01:36:46,060
[SPEAKER_01] jer da je zbog mene vrat u Hrvatskoj.

1692
01:36:46,060 --> 01:36:47,479
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću samo reći,

1693
01:36:47,479 --> 01:36:49,159
[SPEAKER_00] rođeni ste u pravoslavnoj obitelji.

1694
01:36:49,159 --> 01:36:50,100
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1695
01:36:50,100 --> 01:36:52,560
[SPEAKER_01] U meni su spojeni

1696
01:36:52,560 --> 01:36:53,779
[SPEAKER_01] četiri naroda

1697
01:36:53,779 --> 01:36:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] koji se politički

1698
01:36:54,960 --> 01:36:56,260
[SPEAKER_01] idealno ne podnose.

1699
01:36:56,260 --> 01:36:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Rusi, Ukrajinci, Srbi i Hrvati.

1700
01:36:58,960 --> 01:37:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] Evo i u meni ne tukuse.

1701
01:37:00,680 --> 01:37:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1702
01:37:00,920 --> 01:37:02,899
[SPEAKER_01] Jer moji su predstavili

1703
01:37:02,899 --> 01:37:03,859
[SPEAKER_01] ruski brodolomci

1704
01:37:03,859 --> 01:37:04,560
[SPEAKER_01] kod Zadra,

1705
01:37:04,560 --> 01:37:06,340
[SPEAKER_01] pa su se nastanili tu,

1706
01:37:06,340 --> 01:37:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa su se onda

1707
01:37:07,119 --> 01:37:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] priklonili zbog pravoslavlja

1708
01:37:09,199 --> 01:37:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] Srpskoj pravoslavnoj crkvi,

1709
01:37:10,699 --> 01:37:12,800
[SPEAKER_01] a ima ih i Ukrajinaca

1710
01:37:12,800 --> 01:37:13,340
[SPEAKER_01] i Rusa

1711
01:37:13,340 --> 01:37:14,399
[SPEAKER_01] koji se zovu Bundala

1712
01:37:14,399 --> 01:37:15,220
[SPEAKER_01] do danas tamo.

1713
01:37:15,220 --> 01:37:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] Odla ova negdje

1714
01:37:16,039 --> 01:37:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] po prilici dolazi.

1715
01:37:17,539 --> 01:37:19,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa gospodine Bundala,

1716
01:37:19,260 --> 01:37:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] pa mislim ovo mi je sad ono,

1717
01:37:21,460 --> 01:37:24,279
[SPEAKER_00] kako se osjećate?

1718
01:37:24,279 --> 01:37:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pogledajte,

1719
01:37:25,460 --> 01:37:27,220
[SPEAKER_01] Rusa, Ukrajinci,

1720
01:37:27,220 --> 01:37:28,500
[SPEAKER_01] Srba i Hrvati ovdje.

1721
01:37:28,500 --> 01:37:28,979
[SPEAKER_01] To ste vi.

1722
01:37:28,979 --> 01:37:29,960
[SPEAKER_01] To sam ja.

1723
01:37:29,960 --> 01:37:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, moguće je takav biti.

1724
01:37:32,220 --> 01:37:34,140
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mi hoćemo evanđelje,

1725
01:37:34,140 --> 01:37:36,439
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako ćemo djavolje ratove,

1726
01:37:36,439 --> 01:37:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] krvarićemo i nestaćemo u ratovima.

1727
01:37:39,659 --> 01:37:42,100
[SPEAKER_01] Jer će ogroman broj ljudi nestati.

1728
01:37:42,100 --> 01:37:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kad metla Božja pomete

1729
01:37:43,539 --> 01:37:45,100
[SPEAKER_01] sav taj sotonski otpad,

1730
01:37:45,100 --> 01:37:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] biće dopušteno sotoni

1731
01:37:46,920 --> 01:37:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] da sve to povuče u pakao,

1732
01:37:48,960 --> 01:37:51,420
[SPEAKER_01] a tad dolazi do obnove svijeta.

1733
01:37:51,420 --> 01:37:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ostaće malo stado.

1734
01:37:52,920 --> 01:37:54,060
[SPEAKER_01] I rekao mi je gospodin

1735
01:37:54,060 --> 01:37:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] tu na ono pitanje za Evropu.

1736
01:37:57,119 --> 01:37:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, Evropa će biti malo stado

1737
01:37:59,760 --> 01:38:03,760
[SPEAKER_01] mojih, kako je rekao,

1738
01:38:03,760 --> 01:38:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] te koje će preživjeti duše.

1739
01:38:08,000 --> 01:38:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] I oni će obnoviti svijet.

1740
01:38:10,199 --> 01:38:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, preoravanje njive čovječanstva.

1741
01:38:12,760 --> 01:38:15,199
[SPEAKER_01] Humanizam je pokazao se

1742
01:38:15,199 --> 01:38:17,100
[SPEAKER_01] u svemu da je sotonizam.

1743
01:38:17,100 --> 01:38:21,760
[SPEAKER_01] Svi njegovi plodovi su sotonski.

1744
01:38:21,760 --> 01:38:25,600
[SPEAKER_01] Humanizam ide iza njega renesansa,

1745
01:38:25,600 --> 01:38:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] obnova.

1746
01:38:26,260 --> 01:38:29,020
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, humanizam stavlja čovjeka

1747
01:38:29,020 --> 01:38:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] na mjesto Hrista u središte.

1748
01:38:30,699 --> 01:38:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] Renesansa, to je stopnova

1749
01:38:33,220 --> 01:38:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] predkršćanskog poganstva.

1750
01:38:35,039 --> 01:38:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, racionalizam,

1751
01:38:37,340 --> 01:38:40,260
[SPEAKER_01] da kršćani odbace duha svetoga,

1752
01:38:40,260 --> 01:38:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] a oni u tajnim društvima

1753
01:38:43,619 --> 01:38:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] se klanjaju sotoni

1754
01:38:45,539 --> 01:38:46,739
[SPEAKER_01] do današnjega dana

1755
01:38:46,739 --> 01:38:48,239
[SPEAKER_01] i vrše volju njegovu.

1756
01:38:48,239 --> 01:38:49,039
[SPEAKER_01] Razumijem.

1757
01:38:49,039 --> 01:38:50,979
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se humanizam

1758
01:38:50,979 --> 01:38:54,779
[SPEAKER_01] preobražava u socijalizam

1759
01:38:54,779 --> 01:38:56,279
[SPEAKER_01] ili društvenjaštvo.

1760
01:38:56,279 --> 01:39:00,319
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je on u sebi isto razdijeljen

1761
01:39:00,319 --> 01:39:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] na nacional i internacional socijalizam,

1762
01:39:02,800 --> 01:39:04,819
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno nacizam i komunizam,

1763
01:39:04,819 --> 01:39:07,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji se međusobno tuku

1764
01:39:07,300 --> 01:39:10,560
[SPEAKER_01] podijelili su sve evropske narode

1765
01:39:10,560 --> 01:39:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] na naciste i komuniste.

1766
01:39:13,619 --> 01:39:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, po nacistima mogu izazvati

1767
01:39:16,260 --> 01:39:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] međunarodne ratove,

1768
01:39:18,500 --> 01:39:22,960
[SPEAKER_01] a po komunistima mogu izazvati

1769
01:39:22,960 --> 01:39:24,199
[SPEAKER_01] građanske ratove.

1770
01:39:24,199 --> 01:39:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, ako nećeš im biti poslušan,

1771
01:39:26,960 --> 01:39:28,699
[SPEAKER_01] napravit će ti, recimo,

1772
01:39:28,699 --> 01:39:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] u konkretnom našem slučaju,

1773
01:39:30,180 --> 01:39:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] novi rat sa Srbijom i Srbima

1774
01:39:32,460 --> 01:39:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] ili će ti napraviti

1775
01:39:34,840 --> 01:39:35,939
[SPEAKER_01] ovih drugih

1776
01:39:35,939 --> 01:39:38,840
[SPEAKER_01] građanski rat u Zagrebu

1777
01:39:38,840 --> 01:39:40,680
[SPEAKER_01] i u velikim gradovima u Hrvatskoj.

1778
01:39:40,680 --> 01:39:42,020
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, to će ti napraviti

1779
01:39:42,020 --> 01:39:43,479
[SPEAKER_01] socijalizam.

1780
01:39:43,619 --> 01:39:45,920
[SPEAKER_01] I pitanje je kako će ovo izići.

1781
01:39:45,920 --> 01:39:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] Mogli bismo proći

1782
01:39:47,340 --> 01:39:48,399
[SPEAKER_01] kao Sadam Hussein,

1783
01:39:48,399 --> 01:39:50,840
[SPEAKER_01] kao Gadafi,

1784
01:39:50,840 --> 01:39:52,420
[SPEAKER_01] sve su bili saveznici.

1785
01:39:52,420 --> 01:39:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] Njihovi kad su izvršili zločine,

1786
01:39:54,840 --> 01:39:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] ostali su krivi,

1787
01:39:56,000 --> 01:39:57,979
[SPEAKER_01] njih su pobili na isti način

1788
01:39:57,979 --> 01:40:01,739
[SPEAKER_01] kao i ovoga Rusiju 1917.

1789
01:40:01,739 --> 01:40:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ubili su, dakle,

1790
01:40:04,279 --> 01:40:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] jednog oca obitelji,

1791
01:40:06,140 --> 01:40:07,420
[SPEAKER_01] njegovu obitelj,

1792
01:40:07,420 --> 01:40:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] njegov narod

1793
01:40:08,420 --> 01:40:10,079
[SPEAKER_01] i njegovu duhovnost i kulturu,

1794
01:40:10,079 --> 01:40:11,159
[SPEAKER_01] to je s njegovu crpu.

1795
01:40:11,159 --> 01:40:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] Isto su napravili u Iraku,

1796
01:40:13,420 --> 01:40:15,159
[SPEAKER_01] ubili su jednog oca obitelji,

1797
01:40:15,159 --> 01:40:17,060
[SPEAKER_01] ubili su njegove sinove,

1798
01:40:17,060 --> 01:40:21,100
[SPEAKER_01] ubili su njegovu državu

1799
01:40:21,100 --> 01:40:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] i na šta liči danas Irak.

1800
01:40:24,619 --> 01:40:26,579
[SPEAKER_01] To su isto napravili ista stvar,

1801
01:40:26,579 --> 01:40:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] jer se radi o magiji.

1802
01:40:27,720 --> 01:40:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] I sa ovim Gadafijem.

1803
01:40:31,420 --> 01:40:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ubili su oca obitelji,

1804
01:40:34,300 --> 01:40:36,239
[SPEAKER_01] ubili su njegove sinovi jednog sina,

1805
01:40:36,239 --> 01:40:37,260
[SPEAKER_01] mislim da su ubili, da.

1806
01:40:37,260 --> 01:40:39,220
[SPEAKER_01] Ubili su njegov narod,

1807
01:40:39,220 --> 01:40:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji ga je volio i koji je bio miran

1808
01:40:41,300 --> 01:40:42,319
[SPEAKER_01] i zadovoljan s time.

1809
01:40:42,319 --> 01:40:44,220
[SPEAKER_01] I što sad imaš tamo?

1810
01:40:44,300 --> 01:40:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] Svugdje su buktinje terorizma

1811
01:40:46,039 --> 01:40:47,180
[SPEAKER_01] odstali kod su prošli.

1812
01:40:47,380 --> 01:40:47,979
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli ste,

1813
01:40:47,979 --> 01:40:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] u vama teče Ruska,

1814
01:40:49,420 --> 01:40:50,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ukrajinska,

1815
01:40:50,359 --> 01:40:52,680
[SPEAKER_00] Srpska i Hrvatska krv.

1816
01:40:52,680 --> 01:40:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1817
01:40:53,600 --> 01:40:56,359
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vas boli srce kad se sad događa

1818
01:40:56,359 --> 01:40:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] već više od dvije godine

1819
01:40:58,180 --> 01:41:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj strašni rat u Ukrajini?

1820
01:41:00,960 --> 01:41:01,720
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš šta,

1821
01:41:01,720 --> 01:41:03,859
[SPEAKER_01] boli me srce što se uopće

1822
01:41:03,859 --> 01:41:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] u ljudskom rodu događa nešto tako.

1823
01:41:05,960 --> 01:41:07,500
[SPEAKER_01] I Božje srce plače.

1824
01:41:07,500 --> 01:41:10,659
[SPEAKER_01] Potrebno je obraćenje

1825
01:41:10,659 --> 01:41:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] da bi Bog rekao

1826
01:41:12,720 --> 01:41:15,039
[SPEAKER_01] e, sad je vaše vrijeme završeno.

1827
01:41:15,039 --> 01:41:16,819
[SPEAKER_01] Zločinac je napravio zločin,

1828
01:41:16,819 --> 01:41:18,319
[SPEAKER_01] sud Božji može početi.

1829
01:41:18,319 --> 01:41:20,659
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ne ljudski sud ne počinje

1830
01:41:20,659 --> 01:41:22,720
[SPEAKER_01] prije nego što se zločin ne dogodi.

1831
01:41:23,199 --> 01:41:24,680
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je dopušteno Sotoni

1832
01:41:24,680 --> 01:41:26,800
[SPEAKER_01] i Sotonistima da oni svoje naprave

1833
01:41:26,800 --> 01:41:29,800
[SPEAKER_01] pa su sami sebe osudili.

1834
01:41:29,800 --> 01:41:33,140
[SPEAKER_01] A onda Bog uzima svoj narod.

1835
01:41:33,140 --> 01:41:33,979
[SPEAKER_01] Jel?

1836
01:41:33,979 --> 01:41:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] I to će se dogoditi.

1837
01:41:36,279 --> 01:41:39,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam pitao kako ostati živ,

1838
01:41:39,699 --> 01:41:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] onda mi je došla pomoć Božja.

1839
01:41:42,039 --> 01:41:44,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ja sav se sakrijem u Boga,

1840
01:41:44,560 --> 01:41:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] Sotona u Boga ući ne može

1841
01:41:46,619 --> 01:41:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa me ne može ni naći

1842
01:41:47,880 --> 01:41:49,100
[SPEAKER_01] a kamoli mi naškoditi

1843
01:41:49,100 --> 01:41:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] i tako je bilo.

1844
01:41:50,460 --> 01:41:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] U mom životu je tako bilo.

1845
01:41:52,800 --> 01:41:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam najljepše na ovom svjedočenju.

1846
01:41:54,399 --> 01:41:55,840
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome,

1847
01:41:55,840 --> 01:41:57,399
[SPEAKER_01] moguće je preživjeti,

1848
01:41:57,399 --> 01:42:00,439
[SPEAKER_01] ali tražimo ljubav,

1849
01:42:00,439 --> 01:42:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] a ne mržnju.

1850
01:42:01,420 --> 01:42:02,399
[SPEAKER_01] Tražimo jedinstvo,

1851
01:42:02,399 --> 01:42:04,399
[SPEAKER_01] a ne ovoga...

1852
01:42:05,819 --> 01:42:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] Podjele.

1853
01:42:06,359 --> 01:42:06,979
[SPEAKER_01] Podjele.

1854
01:42:06,979 --> 01:42:09,159
[SPEAKER_01] Razmišljam isto ovdje ovaj rat

1855
01:42:09,159 --> 01:42:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] što se dogodio,

1856
01:42:09,960 --> 01:42:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] što je toliko zla napravio

1857
01:42:11,880 --> 01:42:14,319
[SPEAKER_01] i srbima i hrvatsima

1858
01:42:14,319 --> 01:42:15,779
[SPEAKER_01] i bosanskim muslimanima

1859
01:42:15,779 --> 01:42:17,720
[SPEAKER_01] koji su se sad prozvali bošnjaci.

1860
01:42:17,720 --> 01:42:19,420
[SPEAKER_01] Bošnjaci su inače ljudi iz Bosne.

1861
01:42:19,420 --> 01:42:21,899
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš hrvatsko prezime Bošnjak,

1862
01:42:21,899 --> 01:42:22,659
[SPEAKER_01] isto se zove.

1863
01:42:22,880 --> 01:42:27,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi koliko je ljudi pobijeno

1864
01:42:27,579 --> 01:42:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] i koja je mržnja zasijana među nama

1865
01:42:31,420 --> 01:42:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] i koliko je izbjeglica otišlo vani

1866
01:42:35,260 --> 01:42:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] koji se spremaju za povratak

1867
01:42:38,300 --> 01:42:40,739
[SPEAKER_01] na svoja stoljetnja ognjišta

1868
01:42:40,739 --> 01:42:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] u te zemlje.

1869
01:42:42,039 --> 01:42:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] I u Hrvatsku i u Srbiju

1870
01:42:43,920 --> 01:42:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] i u Bosnu i Hercegovinu.

1871
01:42:46,800 --> 01:42:50,199
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite da smo gradili prijateljstvo

1872
01:42:50,199 --> 01:42:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] u Božjem duhu,

1873
01:42:52,260 --> 01:42:54,060
[SPEAKER_01] a ne u interesnom duhu

1874
01:42:54,060 --> 01:42:57,020
[SPEAKER_01] išli najvećem zaštitniku

1875
01:42:57,020 --> 01:42:59,600
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda smo mi kao,

1876
01:42:59,600 --> 01:43:00,439
[SPEAKER_01] kako se to zove,

1877
01:43:00,439 --> 01:43:02,560
[SPEAKER_01] saveznici.

1878
01:43:02,560 --> 01:43:03,680
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo saveznici,

1879
01:43:03,680 --> 01:43:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] nego robovi i vazali.

1880
01:43:06,119 --> 01:43:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sjećam se kada je Tuđman rekao

1881
01:43:09,000 --> 01:43:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] ući ćemo u krug zemalja,

1882
01:43:12,039 --> 01:43:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] slobodnog svijeta.

1883
01:43:13,300 --> 01:43:15,439
[SPEAKER_01] A meni se odljelo iz srca,

1884
01:43:15,439 --> 01:43:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] e moj Franjo,

1885
01:43:16,859 --> 01:43:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] da ti sjedneš s njima

1886
01:43:18,079 --> 01:43:20,600
[SPEAKER_01] za kau popiti.

1887
01:43:20,600 --> 01:43:23,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ti moraš imati petstotina godina

1888
01:43:23,020 --> 01:43:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] kolonija i interkontinentalne

1889
01:43:27,920 --> 01:43:30,859
[SPEAKER_01] more prolivene krvi

1890
01:43:30,859 --> 01:43:33,920
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su oni došli do te moći.

1891
01:43:33,920 --> 01:43:35,699
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, prema tome,

1892
01:43:35,699 --> 01:43:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] žao mi je slavenskih naroda

1893
01:43:37,760 --> 01:43:39,600
[SPEAKER_01] i molim da Bog spasi

1894
01:43:39,600 --> 01:43:41,600
[SPEAKER_01] taj dobri, gostoljubivi

1895
01:43:41,600 --> 01:43:43,060
[SPEAKER_01] i Bogu vjerni narod

1896
01:43:43,060 --> 01:43:46,140
[SPEAKER_01] koji je preživio teror komunizma

1897
01:43:46,140 --> 01:43:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] i nije propala crkva.

1898
01:43:48,079 --> 01:43:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko stoljeća krvare

1899
01:43:53,260 --> 01:43:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] kršćanski narodi na našem terenu.

1900
01:43:55,539 --> 01:43:57,300
[SPEAKER_01] Zato je moj zavijet prvi

1901
01:43:57,300 --> 01:43:59,319
[SPEAKER_01] i zauvijek ostaje.

1902
01:43:59,319 --> 01:44:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] Molio sam gospodine,

1903
01:44:00,880 --> 01:44:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] učini moje srce.

1904
01:44:02,579 --> 01:44:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] Želim da moje srce bude

1905
01:44:05,079 --> 01:44:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] melem na rani

1906
01:44:07,460 --> 01:44:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] tvojega srca

1907
01:44:08,800 --> 01:44:10,619
[SPEAKER_01] zbog istočnog raskola.

1908
01:44:10,619 --> 01:44:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I prvi svetac što sam ga praktično upoznao

1909
01:44:14,000 --> 01:44:16,939
[SPEAKER_01] sa svojim čudesima u mojom obitelji

1910
01:44:16,939 --> 01:44:19,220
[SPEAKER_01] je bio sveti Leopog Bogdan Mandić

1911
01:44:19,220 --> 01:44:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji je naisto to molio.

1912
01:44:21,159 --> 01:44:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam najljepša.

1913
01:44:22,500 --> 01:44:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu hvala.

1914
01:44:24,079 --> 01:44:26,319
[SPEAKER_01] Mir je tu, samo u njega treba ući,

1915
01:44:26,319 --> 01:44:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali moraš djavla izbaciti srca

1916
01:44:28,619 --> 01:44:30,020
[SPEAKER_01] i iz pameti.

1917
01:44:30,020 --> 01:44:33,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ponovite ovo više puta,

1918
01:44:33,680 --> 01:44:35,979
[SPEAKER_00] a onda mi se vrlo brzo vidimo

1919
01:44:35,979 --> 01:44:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] i u novom podcastu Mrežnica.

1920
01:44:37,720 --> 01:44:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam počela, rekla sam

1921
01:44:39,159 --> 01:44:40,659
[SPEAKER_00] tko ima uši, neka čuje.

1922
01:44:40,659 --> 01:44:42,100
[SPEAKER_00] S time ću i završiti.

1923
01:44:42,239 --> 01:44:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] Tko ima uši, neka čuje.

